   Purpose: Styles the Looper/Consumer-based shop page as
            a luxury editorial product grid with inline
            variation selection via Quick Add. Cards stay
            clean and editorial by default — the add-to-cart
            form is hidden until the user clicks "Quick Add",
            then quantity controls, price, and button fade in
            once a variation is selected.

   What this does:
   1. PAGE — White background, hides default WooCommerce
      sorting, grid toggle, and result count.
   2. CARD — Clean edges, subtle neutral shadow, white bg.
   3. TITLE — Cormorant Garamond italic, centered, with
