      and button are hidden until a variation is selected
      (class .ft-variation-selected on the wrap), then
      fade in. For simple products, the button is always
      visible.
   8. STOCK — "In stock" hidden. Out-of-stock shows as
      minimal quiet uppercase label in muted gray.
   9. QUANTITY — Ultra-light editorial +/- glyphs, centered.
   10. BUTTON — Warm taupe, full-width, hover lift.
